Prioritize clean anatomy, believable joints, readable hands, and natural body proportions.

// Your Prompt
{cursor}

// utility cleanup
Prioritize a clean, attractive, symmetrical, expressive face with readable eyes and mouth.

// Your Prompt
{cursor}

// utility cleanup
Prioritize correct hand anatomy, natural finger count, and believable hand gestures.

// Your Prompt
{cursor}

